{"tid":2312861,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MMA 2020︱BTS防彈少年團6缺1出席失色　肺炎確診歌手都「現身」","createTime":"2020-12-05T10:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T12:26:14.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"92aab7e421b329ecdefcdcccd1e8e76a6dcda060","tid":2312861,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"韓國頒獎典禮「Melon Music Awards 2020」（甜瓜音樂獎、簡稱MMA），今年受新冠肺炎疫情影響，轉陣以網上轉播形式舉行。雖然隔住熒幕，但紅地氈一樣熱鬧，BTS防彈少年團、IZ*ONE、Oh My Girl和MONSTA X等照樣有盛裝出席。<br />\n<br />\n女團方面IZ*ONE和Oh My Girl都有全員現身，齊齊大曬美腿。而男團方面BTS防彈少年團Suga因手術後正在休養當中，今年6缺1出席略為失色，但都有MONSTA X、TXT和THE BOYZ等組合撐場。由於今年頒獎禮和紅地氈都以預錄方式進行，因此可見到早前確診新冠肺炎的24歲Trot歌手李燦元都有參與，畫面搞笑。"},{"pid":"41c4151e52445675b593c53f47d284ae24531912","tid":2312861,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T10:26:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201205/411952706886832128184736.jpeg/8eaxCawdNfiAd-H6dfoY3PmgaYRuvQ6z1_RpGdf0aRk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201205%2F411952706886832128184736.jpeg%2F8eaxCawdNfiAd-H6dfoY3PmgaYRuvQ6z1_RpGdf0aRk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b9d678ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201205/411952721458630656863547.jpeg/-s5S3DALAQG3oZ4B0fuvE84nPN2WOdvusDuAabA7gGk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201205%2F411952721458630656863547.jpeg%2F-s5S3DALAQG3oZ4B0fuvE84nPN2WOdvusDuAabA7gGk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=34238508&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bff9cac8e742558142cd3545af0f8ca1ad903b76","tid":2312861,"uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T10:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201205/411952438455570432261358.jpeg/ct86hAlBL2LpTLuSjr2azl7ac6NqZIL9cqCKmHKgipg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01